  "intent": "Perform peptide mass spectrometry sample preparation using SP2 bead-based cleanup on up to 48 samples in deep-well plates. Add specified volumes of SP2 beads to samples, execute three sequential acetonitrile wash cycles with magnetic separation (5-minute engagements at defined height), remove supernatants between washes. Elute peptides with elution buffer using 25-cycle mixing, transfer eluates to PCR plate wells, then add formic acid and iRT standards at specified volumes for MS analysis preparation.",
